    Nd4jCpu

    @Namespace(value="sd::ops")
public static class Nd4jCpu.subtract
extends Nd4jCpu.BroadcastableOp
    This is one of auto-broadcastable operations. It accepts 2 operands, and operation is applied based on their shapes: 1) if shapes are equal that's pairwise operation, result will have the same shape. 2) if shape X is scalar and shape Y is array - result will have shape equal to Y. 3) if shape X is array and shape Y is scalar - result will have shape equal to X. 4) if shape X and Y are both arrays, but shapes aren't equal - result shape will be broadcast result. This operation returns Z = Subtract(X, Y)
